In the midst of rushing to pick up my family members from the airport, I allowed my impatience to override my better judgment. I was driving aggressively and at a speed above the permitted limit. Moreover, I made the irresponsible decision to answer a text message from my cousin while behind the wheel. It is with great remorse that I admit my actions resulted in a collision with a guardrail.

